During those times traveling should all be pre-arranged  and need to get permission  from the local authority with a qualified tour guides. We cannot just explore on our own (especially ladies). I’ve seen the Saudi’s transformation from a very conservative country to a more open one and how it progressed and developed to a modern one.  I’m so happy for the huge change for the better especially for the women. Keep it up Saudi. Shout out to all my friends and colleagues in KSA! On another note, Eva you’re such an inspiration to all the women that you’re empowering on. I enjoy watching your vlogs and I have to catch up more. You’re so brave and fearless.
